title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - week 33
description:
In this video, we'll explore the latest additions to the MSFS 2020 marketplace. This week, there's a treasure trove for general aviation enthusiasts with multiple aircrafts joining the marketplace. The exciting part? Two of these new aircrafts come as a bundle, offering an attractive discount.

In addition to the aircrafts, a handful of airports have been updated, and several mission packs have been launched for both small aircrafts and larger airliners.

For those who are fans of history, there's more good news. Alongside the release of an "older" aircraft, several packs have been introduced that will transport you back to the year 1935.
